            <p class="base-aside-card__subtitle font-sans text-sm text-color-text leading-regular break-words overflow-anywhere
                line-clamp-2">
              
          UK Software Engineers saved from the AI jobs carnage.

At least, based on my reasoning.

Follow me on this.

You pay for £100 worth of code.   For arguments sake, it's a CRUD service.  Similar have already been created for the project.

For £100 a UK Software Engineer gets 25% complete
for £100 an overseas Software Engineer gets 50% complete
for £100 UK Software Engineer AI assisted gets 75% complete
For £100 overseas Software Engineer AI assisted gets 100% complete

Result without AI: Overseas is 50% cheaper for the same work.

Result with AI: Overseas is 25% cheaper for the same work.

More AI = less advantage to Offshoring

AI brings home Software Engineering and Testing which was previously outsourced or offshored.


#recruitment
#jobs
#AIdoomsterschokeontheirflawedargument
        
            </p>

