          The UK-US Tech Prosperity Deal is set to reshape the hiring landscape in the UK.

Here are a few key changes we’re expecting:

1/ 120,000 new GPUs → demand will rise for AI/ML engineers and infrastructure specialists.
2/ AI Growth Zones → new regional hubs (like the North East) will see concentrated hiring activity.
3/ Salary pressure → competition for scarce skills could push compensation upwards.
4/ Long-term planning → 3–5 year pipelines will become as important as today’s hires.

At Arc, we’re already working with clients and candidates to prepare:
 ✔️ Identifying and securing AI/compute talent early
 ✔️ Tracking how comp and skills trends are shifting
 ✔️ Supporting specialists as they plan their next career moves
The infrastructure investment is huge — but it’s people who will make it succeed.

#TechHiring #AIJobs #UKUSTechDeal #Recruitment #ExecutiveSearch #Search #TalentStrategy #ArcSelect #ArcITRecruitment
        
            </p>

